   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 2411, recto: (1) I, John, (2) son of Pesenthius, (3) the man of Terkot, write (4) to Pegosh, son of (5) Manasseh, the man of Jeme.  I owe (6) you one artaba of wheat (7) and its interest, which is (8) one ment of wheat, and (9) I shall give it to you in Paone.  (10) I, John, (11) son of Methusela, (12) wrote (13) this sherd on (14) the eighth (15) of Thoth.</ab>
